                     <interp inst="t18291029-156-off877" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291029-156-cd878" type="crimeDate">27th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-156-off877 t18291029-156-cd878"></join>, 1 cap, value 3s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18291029-156-victim1240" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Rowe
                     <interp inst="t18291029-156-victim1240" type="surname" value="Rowe"></interp>
